      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SUPER SEALANT (1) finds it hard to win but looks close to breaking through. Has been in the minors the last two runs, the latest finishing third (24.73) at this track. Key chance in this line up. JACK'S REGRET (4) jumped from a middle draw last time and could manage only fourth and beaten 3 lengths (24.66) at this track. Some good form is emerging from his last run. In the mix. DESTINI LORENZO (8) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing sixth (26.22) in a Grade 5 at Shepparton. Has a good record at this journey. The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. Must be included in calculations. SLINGER (2) has ability and can feature with the right run after missing a cheque here most recently.",
